flowchart LR
  SRC[Source<br/>skill / MCP / CLI / adapter]
  CAP[Capability<br/>reviewed action]
  REQ[Request]
  REV[Review]
  APP[Approval<br/>agent cannot approve itself]
  AUD[Audit]
  CFG[Config version]
  ACT[Next-run activation]

  SRC --> CAP
  CAP --> REQ --> REV --> APP --> AUD --> CFG --> ACT
